						               													<description>A weather board game that uses a voice assistant.&amp;#10;Meteoropaths are demanding travelers whose mood changes according to the weather: their goal is to live the ideal holiday by traveling in 7 different locations with the climatic conditions they prefer.&amp;#10;The meteoropaths available for each player are: the tan fanatic (look for places with a temperature of 25-35 degrees Celsius), the ecological backpacker (15-25), the decadent poet (10-20), the yeti (0-10).&amp;#10;Meteoropaths move on the board asking the voice assistant for information on the local weather: if the temperature is ideal for them, they earn a day off. Players are helped by souvenirs and baggage cards that they can conquer during the game.&amp;#10;The meteoropathic who first completes his 7-day vacation wins, also collecting 3 selfies in 3 different continents.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
